<paragraph id="IFRS16_32" base="F45929186"><paranum>32</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 16"/><data name="paranum" value="32"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0118">If the <xref base="F45929685" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0363">lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0214"/></ph></xref> transfers ownership of the <xref base="F45929849" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0392">underlying asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0373"/></ph></xref> to the <xref base="F45929736" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0380">lessee<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0220"/></ph></xref> by the end of the <xref base="F45929725" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0376">lease term<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0218"/></ph></xref> or if the cost of the <xref base="F45929827" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0388">right-of-use asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0342"/></ph></xref> reflects that the lessee will exercise a purchase option, the lessee shall depreciate the right-of-use asset from the <xref base="SL45930024" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0349">commencement date<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0037"/></ph></xref> to the end of the <xref base="F45929893" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0400"><i>useful life</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0380"/></ph></xref> of the underlying asset. Otherwise, the lessee shall depreciate the right-of-use asset from the commencement date to the earlier of the end of the <i>useful life</i> of the right-of-use asset or the end of the lease term.</p></body></paragraph>